					"elementDisplay": "<p chunk_id=\"2857339d-9236-4d52-9517-f0de85657410\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Prerequisite:</span></strong> <tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"distracting-illusion\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Distracting Illusion</tooltip> talent</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"1e6a11a0-a1a4-40bf-8ddf-f6463d4339d0\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Act</span></strong><strong><span class=\"color-span\">ivation:</span></strong> <span aria-label=\"Two Actions\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"Two Actions\">2</span></p>\n<div chunk_id=\"e73e9f29-0daa-437a-8a62-da1c419c443d\" class=\"lore-block\" style=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><em>You create a brief burst of light and sound that attacks the senses of targets near you.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p chunk_id=\"f2446140-e3a5-4e49-9827-c7b1da7ffb82\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">Spend 1 <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"investiture\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Investiture</tooltip> to project a burst of light in an area within your reach, up to the size you can create with your ranks in Illumination. Make one Illumination test and compare the result against the Cognitive defense of each character in that area. If you succeed against a target, they become <tooltip category=\"condition\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"disoriented\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Disoriented</tooltip> until the end of their next turn.</p>",
