							"value": "<p chunk_id=\"4ca8fac2-abc5-4271-995b-29fed2281797\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Prerequisite:</span></strong>\n<tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"multiplicative-lightweaving\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Multiplicative Lightweaving</tooltip> talent or <tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"spiritual-illumination\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Spiritual Illumination</tooltip> talent\n</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"ef2de767-e5e6-4134-ae45-b78abba702aa\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Act</span></strong><strong><span class=\"color-span\">ivation:</span></strong> <span aria-label=\"Always Active\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"Always Active\">∞</span></p>\n<div chunk_id=\"1b9f1a96-1076-4cc6-97b3-f394f0d0a5f0\" class=\"lore-block\" style=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><em>You’ve become so efficient at powering your illusions that you can maintain them indefinitely.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p chunk_id=\"ce9026af-535f-48c6-ae77-d318e10b4da3\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">While you have 1 Investiture or more, each of your Illumination infusions within your spren bond range expends no infused Investiture at the start of your turn.</p>",
